data.description: Located across from the new high school,  4 bdrm, 2 bath rambler with master walk-in closet, main floor family room with vaulted ceiling, and a 3 car heated garage. . Kitchen open to the living dining area and has newer tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and walk-in pantry with option for main floor laundry hook ups. Lower level theater room furniture and large TV entertainment center is negotiable. Fenced back yard has a 10x12 shed.
